<p>This course delivers a strong understanding of climate science. It combines it with relevant knowledge about ocean-atmosphere interaction, insight into global change, sustainability, air and water quality and climate change mitigation measures. This combination is ideally suited to equip you with the knowledge required to tackle the mounting challenges in sea level change mitigation, local climate adaptation, sustainable resource management and coastal ocean climate mitigation. </p>
