<h2 id="why-choose-this-course">Why choose this course?</h2>
<p>In today’s fast-paced digital world, businesses are constantly looking for ways to work smarter, not harder. Roles in automation and process analytics are rapidly growing, with organisations across industries investing in digital transformation to improve efficiency and reduce costs. </p>
