<p>This major equips you with a powerful combination of technical and analytical skills to thrive in a range of high-demand careers. You''ll work with real-world data to solve practical problems, develop strong process modelling skills, and contribute to building smarter, more sustainable organisations. With the rise of digital transformation across sectors like manufacturing, finance, healthcare, and IT, graduates with skills in process analytics and automation are becoming increasingly sought-after. Whether you''re interested in analysis, design, consulting, or project management, this major opens the door to a wide variety of meaningful career pathways. </p>
<p> </p>
